title: Space Age Funk Music Loop Pack
description: Space Age Funk is a jam-packed album of groovy funky pop tunes and loops with a retro twist, written for game & app developers!
longDescription:
Preview: https://soundcloud.com/user-512388516/space-age-funk-video-game-music-loop-pack-for-indie-game-developers

The Space Age Funk Music Loop Pack contains 35 music files and seamless loops clocking in at almost 30 minutes of music!
Excellent for games and apps in the fun, quirky, spacey, hip, children, and anything that promotes that funky groovy feel!
Contains a variety of loop lengths and styles, as well as full mixes for trailers and promotion of your project.
technicalDetails:
Formats included: .wav,
Tracks and seamless looping wav files at 44.100 kHz, 16 Bit, Stereo.
Works on all platforms
